Package org.jscsi.parser

This package provides all main classes which are needed to deserialize and serialize all the messages defined by the iSCSI Standard (RFC 3720).

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AbstractMessageParser AbstractMessageParser Abstract class from which each parser (initiator or target message parser) for a specific Protocol Data Unit (PDU) is inherited.
BasicHeaderSegment BasicHeaderSegment This class encapsulate a Basic Header Segment (BHS), which is defined in the iSCSI Protocol (RFC3720).
Constants Constants This class defines all the constants needed by the parsing and serializing process.
InitiatorMessageParser InitiatorMessageParser This abstract class is the base class of all initiator message parsers defined in the iSCSI Protocol (RFC3720).
MessageParserFactory MessageParserFactory This class creates a specified parser object.
ProtocolDataUnit ProtocolDataUnit This class encapsulates a Protocol Data Unit (PDU), which is defined in the iSCSI Standard (RFC 3720).
ProtocolDataUnitFactory ProtocolDataUnitFactory

A factory to create all supported the ProtocolDataUnit instances.
TargetMessageParser TargetMessageParser This abstract class is the base class of all target message parsers defined in the iSCSI Protocol (RFC3720).
 

Enum Summary
OperationCode OperationCode This enumeration defines all valid operation codes, which are conform to iSCSI Protocol (RFC 3720).
 

Package org.jscsi.parser Description

This package provides all main classes which are needed to deserialize and serialize all the messages defined by the iSCSI Standard (RFC 3720).
